	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There appear not to be precompiled binaries for Mac OS X or for Darwin. I'd just download the cc65 source code tarball from <a href="ftp://ftp.musoftware.de/pub/uz/cc65/" class="postlink">cc65 FTP</a> and follow the instructions.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


